OL,3,CEngland fans say Mexico win builds
OL,4,Cmomentum to beat Norway and lift World
OL,5,CCup
OL,7,FEngland fans said the Three Lions'
OL,8,Fdramatic victory over Mexico has
OL,9,Fconvinced them the team has the
OL,10,Fmomentum to beat Norway and even win
OL,11,Fthe World Cup.
OL,13,FMore than 10,000 supporters from the
OL,14,FUK are set to descend on the Hard Rock
OL,15,FStadium in Miami on Saturday, with
OL,16,FEngland and Norway fans already
OL,17,Fcreating a party atmosphere across
OL,18,FSouth Beach.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
