OL,3,CEngland fans say Mexico win builds
OL,4,Cmomentum to beat Norway and lift World
OL,5,CCup
OL,7,FThree Lions fans were enjoying
OL,8,Fthemselves at the bars on Friday
OL,9,Fevening after Norway fans took part in
OL,10,Ftheir now-infamous row on the
OL,11,Foceanfront.
OL,13,FPolice back in the UK will no longer
OL,14,Fhave to deal with an early hours
OL,15,Fscreening of the game following the
OL,16,Fdelayed 2am kick-off against Mexico.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
