OL,3,CEngland fans say Mexico win builds
OL,4,Cmomentum to beat Norway and lift World
OL,5,CCup
OL,7,FThe latest figures from the UK
OL,8,FFootball Policing Unit (UKFPU) showed
OL,9,Fthere were 42 football-related arrests
OL,10,Facross the country during the round of
OL,11,F16 win, with officers responding to
OL,12,F223 football-related incidents.
OL,14,FThe number of incidents responded to
OL,15,Fincreased from 142 incidents during
OL,16,Fthe previous match against the
OL,17,FDemocratic Republic of Congo.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
