OL,3,CEngland fans say Mexico win builds
OL,4,Cmomentum to beat Norway and lift World
OL,5,CCup
OL,7,FChief Constable Mark Roberts said:
OL,8,F"The UKFPU is collating the
OL,9,Finformation received from UK police
OL,10,Fforces, but the early indications are
OL,11,Fthat there were significant numbers of
OL,12,Fcalls to licenced premises, around
OL,13,Fviolence and disorder, which can be
OL,14,Fattributed to the extended licensing
OL,15,Fhours."
OL,17,FOn South Beach on Friday, however,
OL,18,FEngland supporters were focused on
OL,19,Fwhat they hope will be another step
OL,20,Ftowards ending the country's long wait
OL,21,Ffor major tournament success.
