OL,3,CEngland fans say Mexico win builds
OL,4,Cmomentum to beat Norway and lift World
OL,5,CCup
OL,7,FDylan Kayek, 22, from Manchester, who
OL,8,Fnow lives in Miami, told the Press
OL,9,FAssociation: "I'm very confident. Not
OL,10,Ftoo confident, but I feel good about
OL,11,Fus winning, definitely."
OL,13,FJosh Taylor, 22, added: "I think I
OL,14,Fagree. We're on a good run, we're
OL,15,Fbuilding momentum into the tournament
OL,16,Fso hopefully we just keep it going."
OL,18,FRuth Kayek, 48, said simply: "It's
OL,19,Fcoming home."
