OL,3,CEngland fans say Mexico win builds
OL,4,Cmomentum to beat Norway and lift World
OL,5,CCup
OL,7,F"I think we're just going to keep it
OL,8,Fgoing, build momentum," he said.
OL,10,F"The big players are turning up.
OL,11,FBellingham, Kane ` I hope they get it
OL,12,Fdone tomorrow."
OL,14,FMr Taylor added: "We'll be here
OL,15,Ftomorrow night after England win and
OL,16,Fwe'll be going crazy."
OL,18,FAsked whether she would travel to New
OL,19,FYork should England reach the World
OL,20,FCup final, Mrs Kayek said: "Damn
OL,21,Fright. I'm going with or without them."
