OL,5,CCup
OL,7,FJack Williamson, 32, from Wiltshire,
OL,8,Fsaid stopping Haaland will be key.
OL,10,F"I reckon if we can keep Haaland
OL,11,Fquiet, we'll be all right," he told PA.
OL,13,F"I think we'll control the game,
OL,14,Fhopefully nick a couple of goals. 2-0.
OL,15,FPut your money on it."
OL,17,FMr Williamson continued: "I wouldn't
OL,18,Flike to call it too early but it's a
OL,19,Fgame we probably should win.
