OL,5,CCup
OL,7,F"They'll be tricky, but looking at
OL,8,FEngland, we should beat them."
OL,10,FJosh Dolman, 34, from Swindon, added:
OL,11,F"I reckon it'll be easier than people
OL,12,Fthink. I think a 3-1, they'll score a
OL,13,Flate goal, but we're much better than
OL,14,Fthey are."
OL,16,FMr Dolman, who only booked his flights
OL,17,Fto Miami on Tuesday after England beat
OL,18,FMexico, said: "I couldn't resist.
OL,19,FCould not resist after that Mexico
OL,20,Fgame.
