OL,3,CEngland fans say Mexico win builds
OL,4,Cmomentum to beat Norway and lift World
OL,5,CCup
OL,7,F"We're going to win it all so I
OL,8,Fcouldn't miss it out in Miami.
OL,10,F"It's the missus who convinced me to
OL,11,Fcome. She said 'you'll regret it
OL,12,Fforever if you don't go'.
OL,14,F"We did the Euros final and lost that
OL,15,Fand I just couldn't not come."
OL,17,FDespite his optimism, he admitted
OL,18,FEngland rarely make knockout football
OL,19,Fstraightforward.
