OL,7,FHe continued: "Even though I said it
OL,8,Fwith confidence earlier, it's never
OL,9,Fnormal with England.
OL,11,F"So there'll be something that throws
OL,12,Fa little spanner in the works, like
OL,13,Fthat Mexico game.
OL,15,F"When we go 3-1 up, then we concede,
OL,16,Fthen we get someone sent off ` it's
OL,17,Fnever normal.
