OL,7,F"So whatever happens, it's going to be
OL,8,Fa little bit weird, but I'm hoping
OL,9,Fit's just a nice, normal, easy 2-0 or
OL,10,F3-0 or 3-1."
OL,12,FMr Williamson believes victory on
OL,13,FSaturday could pave the way for
OL,14,Ftournament success.
OL,16,FHe said: "If we can get past Norway,
OL,17,Fthen there's every chance we win the
OL,18,Flot."
