OL,7,FMr Williamson joked: "If England are
OL,8,Fto win a tournament, one way to do it
OL,9,Fis with a German in charge."
OL,11,FMr Dolman replied: "Typical England
OL,12,Fthat we can't do it and we need a bit
OL,13,Fof help."
OL,15,FJayden Johal, 21, from just outside
OL,16,FLondon, also expects England to
OL,17,Fprogress, although he believes Norway
OL,18,Fwill be a tough test.
OL,20,F"I think it'll be tough, but I see us
OL,21,Fdoing it," he said.
