OL,7,F"Maybe extra time, but I think we'll
OL,8,Fget it done."
OL,10,FHis friend Alex Gabbitas, 22, from
OL,11,Fnorth-west London, said they had not
OL,12,Fyet booked travel for a possible semi-
OL,13,Ffinal.
OL,15,F"No, not yet. It's on the cards. But
OL,16,Fwe do have accommodation in New York
OL,17,Fso preferably get there," he said.
OL,19,F"That's tomorrow's plan. Tomorrow's
OL,20,Fproblem."
