OL,3,CEngland fans say Mexico win builds
OL,4,Cmomentum to beat Norway and lift World
OL,5,CCup
OL,7,FEngland assistant manager Anthony
OL,8,FBarry said on Friday that it was time
OL,9,Ffor England to "take the handbrake
OL,10,Foff", insisting the squad still had
OL,11,Fanother level to reach as they chase a
OL,12,Fplace in the semi-finals.
OL,14,FSir David Beckham also spoke to
OL,15,FEngland's players on the eve of their
OL,16,Fcrunch World Cup quarter-final against
OL,17,FNorway.
