OL,7,FThe 51-year-old star was in attendance
OL,8,Ffor a training session in Fort
OL,9,FLauderdale and spoke to players in the
OL,10,Fgym before they took to the field.
OL,12,FVictory over Norway would send England
OL,13,Finto a semi-final against either
OL,14,FArgentina or Switzerland in Atlanta on
OL,15,FWednesday.
